<p><placeName>Alexandria [Louisiana]</placeName> <date when="1821-12-03">December the 3d 1821</date></p>

<p><persName>Mr David J. Marple</persName> bought of <persName>Nichols Rightor</persName></p>

<p>3 yds Stockenitt at $3.50 ____________________ $10. 50

1 vest Patron __ 3.50_________________________   1. 50
							     _________
							      12. 00</p>

<p>I promise to pay six Months after this date the above Sum of
twelve Dollares as witness My hand&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>David J. Marple</persName></p>

<p><placeName>Colorado </placeName><date when="1822-03-08">March the 8th 1822</date></p>
<p>For value received I assign the within account (and due bill) to
<persName>Mr. S. F Austin</persName> as witness my hand</p>

<p><persName>N Rightor</persName>    [Rubric]</p>

        </div1>
